description: One of Lala`s twin younger sisters, she is introduced when most of the characters are in a virtual game world created by Lala that she and Momo subsequently modify. Nana has long hair, a single visible sharp tooth and unlike her sisters, a flat chest. She understands and can talk to animals. Like her big sister, she too has cell phone capable of transporting objects, however instead of gadgets Nana summons animals.
name: Nana Astar Deviluke
